## 🏃‍♂️ Getting Started

1. Clone repository:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/jhonatasmatos/15-days-of-playwright.git
```

2. Install dependencies

```bash
npm install
```

3. Run Day 1 test

```bash
npx playwright test tests/day01.test.js
```

## 📂 Project Structure

```text
15-days-of-playwright/
├── tests/               # Test files (day01.test.js, etc.)
├── assets/              # Screenshots/videos
├── playwright.config.js # Configuration
└── package.json         # Dependencies
```

